These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, satire
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | sprite   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | mystery   |
| Sport         | cricket | rowing |
| Transport     | motorbike | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, cherry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, mystery
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, car
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the car##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peach     | cherry |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | crime  |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | goldfish     |
| Transport     | trike   | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the photographer##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | almond-milk     | iced-tea |
| Job         | photographer | firefighter    |
| Pet         | goldfish         | guinea-pig        |
| Transport   | scooter         | boat    |

