.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, entrepreneur
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, french
2 different pets are kept: fish, frog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. the french is on the far left or far right##3
3. the entrepreneur is the thai##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | fisherman    |
| Nationality   | thai       | french |
| Pet           | fish         | frog    |
| Sport         | tennis    | lacrosse   |

