3. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | coffee    |
| Job         | accountant        | software-developer |
| Pet         | mouse          | rabbit     |
| Transport   | scooter        | car     |

 